#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/invoicing_policy.rst:7
msgid ""
"The **Invoice what is ordered** rule is used as **default mode** in Odoo "
"Sales, which means that customers will be invoiced once the sales order "
"is confirmed."
