#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/follow_up/automatic_alerts.rst:71
msgid ""
"This alert is applied to the *Rating Satisfaction* of your customers, and"
" the action is triggered on *Timed condition*. If their satisfaction rate"
" is lower than 50%, a salesperson contacts the customer. This action is "
"automatically assigned to the salesperson who manages the subscription, "
